Mechanical daily stock swing strategy using ATR stops, Heikin Ashi trend confirmation, and Bollinger Bands context. Entries occur above 50 SMA on bullish Heikin Ashi candles; initial stop is 3xATR with trailing stop of highest close minus 2xAtr, reducing to 1.5xATR when profit protection triggers (+2R and momentum weakening). Exits are fully ATR-based, giving a simple, rules-driven approach to ride trends while protecting gains
